  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/eac1248abdd9c8e79ed323990ac4e228.poster.avif?t=1759187208\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/eac1248abdd9c8e79ed323990ac4e228.webm?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/eac1248abdd9c8e79ed323990ac4e228.mp4?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against up to 12 friends in Synth Race. Run, jump, and slide your way to victory across 16 levels featuring a variety of obstacle courses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1-12 Player Lobbies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race with up to 12 other players. Host a public lobby to race against other players from around the world, or host a private lobby for your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 Levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through 16 levels that gradually increase in difficulty. All 16 levels available at time of official release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time Trials</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo in Time Trials to beat the mastery times and top the Leaderboards. Compete among your friends in the Friend Leaderboard or with players from around the world in the Global Leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw attack balls with a variety of debuffs to sabotage other players or punch them off a ledge. Choose between two attack ball modes when setting up a lobby: pick Frenzy mode to automatically receive attack balls for a very chaotic experience, or pick Block mode to collect them as you move through the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cosmetics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete Time Trials and collect tokens hidden in each level to unlock skins and hats that show off your achievements.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/a28df45cfbaa12ef1e7c8fdf81e9b921.poster.avif?t=1759187208\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/a28df45cfbaa12ef1e7c8fdf81e9b921.webm?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/a28df45cfbaa12ef1e7c8fdf81e9b921.mp4?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/0cd3e9917dca5263e46be12cdcc22821.poster.avif?t=1759187208\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/0cd3e9917dca5263e46be12cdcc22821.webm?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/0cd3e9917dca5263e46be12cdcc22821.mp4?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/eac1248abdd9c8e79ed323990ac4e228.poster.avif?t=1759187208\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/eac1248abdd9c8e79ed323990ac4e228.webm?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/eac1248abdd9c8e79ed323990ac4e228.mp4?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against up to 12 friends in Synth Race. Run, jump, and slide your way to victory across 16 levels featuring a variety of obstacle courses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1-12 Player Lobbies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race with up to 12 other players. Host a public lobby to race against other players from around the world, or host a private lobby for your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 Levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through 16 levels that gradually increase in difficulty. All 16 levels available at time of official release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time Trials</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo in Time Trials to beat the mastery times and top the Leaderboards. Compete among your friends in the Friend Leaderboard or with players from around the world in the Global Leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw attack balls with a variety of debuffs to sabotage other players or punch them off a ledge. Choose between two attack ball modes when setting up a lobby: pick Frenzy mode to automatically receive attack balls for a very chaotic experience, or pick Block mode to collect them as you move through the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cosmetics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete Time Trials and collect tokens hidden in each level to unlock skins and hats that show off your achievements.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/a28df45cfbaa12ef1e7c8fdf81e9b921.poster.avif?t=1759187208\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/a28df45cfbaa12ef1e7c8fdf81e9b921.webm?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/a28df45cfbaa12ef1e7c8fdf81e9b921.mp4?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/0cd3e9917dca5263e46be12cdcc22821.poster.avif?t=1759187208\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/0cd3e9917dca5263e46be12cdcc22821.webm?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944360/extras/0cd3e9917dca5263e46be12cdcc22821.mp4?t=1759187208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
